############
Installation
############

****************
Running the demo
****************

* Get the code: ``git clone git@github.com:benoitbryon/minventory.git && cd minventory/``
* Run database (requires Docker): ``make db``
* Run API: ``make api`` (`virtualenv`_ and Python3 recommended)


Inspect the service:

* API is served at http://localhost:5000.


.. _`virtualenv`: https://virtualenv.pypa.io/
